🚀 Exciting news! 

We're hosting a **Gen AI Hackathon & Workshop** at our college! 🌐✨

Join us as we teach students to create a **full-stack web application** using only generative AI. 🛠️💡 

The best part? The top web app creators will get a chance to attend the **Mumbai Tech Fest!** 🎉 

Are you ready to innovate and showcase your skills? Let’s ignite creativity together! 💪 

What ideas do you have for a web app? Share below! 👇
